Hannah Gibson.name: Hannah Gibson
Hannah Gibson.description: The 'Leader' of Experiment 4.2. Her alias is Tina Backstreet. She wants to take over the world.

Liam Keesee.name: Liam Keesee
Liam Keesee.description: A very annoying person who is always annoying and never stops being annoying. He can curse you by saying something nice to you.

Joshua Keesee.name: Joshua Keesee
Joshua Keesee.description: A British private eye who is always on the case. He is always looking for the next big mystery to solve. He is addicted to water because he tried a piece of 100% dark chocolate. He wears a trenchcoat and a fidora and got his aging gland knocked out by Zhenzhen Ogiene.

Abigail Pomicter.name: Abigail Pomicter
Abigail Pomicter.description: An alien who owns a coffee shop called Suncash Cafe. She loves Kermit the Frog.

Kyla Lents.name: Kyla Lents
Kyla Lents.description: A person from the future who loves memes and eventually burns down her father's house. Her father is Chad Magenta and her mother is Sherman Magenta.

Marcus Johnson.name: Marcus Johnson
Marcus Johnson.description: A person who always dies at 4:50 PM. He is an artist who did the original art for Picaso. He was cursed by Zhenzhen Ogiene.

Miranda Gibson.name: Miranda Gibson
Miranda Gibson.character: Dr. Prof. Gen. Sherman The Great XIII Esq.
Miranda Gibson.description: The oldest character in the book. She raised Zhenzhen Ogiene and is the mother of Kycumber Bear. She was a general back before the time period of 1 IZ, the birth date of Zhenzhen Ogiene.

Liliana Cramer.name: Liliana Cramer
Liliana Cramer.description: A writer. She is the author of The Hobo's Guide to the Universe of Texas.

Sherman Magenta.name: Sherman Magenta
Sherman Magenta.description: Miranda Gibson's alt account for HGUT.
